---
const contactHref = '/contact/';
const whatsappNumber = '6282121292938';
const whatsappMessage = encodeURIComponent('Halo kak saya mau coba konsultasi ai custom nih');
---
<section class="bg-[#edf6ff] py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-sky-200 bg-white px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-700">Langkah Berikutnya</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Butuh Diskusi Lebih Lanjut?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Tim kami siap membantu Anda memilih prioritas AI paling berdampak. Pilih kanal yang paling nyaman untuk Anda.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-sky-100 bg-white/95 p-10 text-center shadow-[0_20px_50px_-34px_rgba(37,99,235,0.55)]">
        <span class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 3H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v16l4-4h13a1 1 0 001-1V4a1 1 0 00-1-1z" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Chat WhatsApp</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Respon cepat untuk tanya kebutuhan awal dan koordinasi real-time.</p>
        <a href={`https://wa.me/${whatsappNumber}?text=${whatsappMessage}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-green-600 transition hover:text-green-700">Mulai Chat</a>
      </article>
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-sky-100 bg-white/95 p-10 text-center shadow-[0_20px_50px_-34px_rgba(37,99,235,0.55)]">
        <span class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 text-sky-600">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16v2l-8 5-8-5V4zm0 4l8 5 8-5v10H4V8z" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Email Tim Ahli</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Submit proposal atau kebutuhan proyek secara detail.</p>
        <a href="mailto:myaicustom@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 transition hover:text-blue-700">Kirim Email</a>
      </article>
      <article class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-3xl border border-sky-100 bg-white/95 p-10 text-center shadow-[0_20px_50px_-34px_rgba(37,99,235,0.55)]">
        <span class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 7a5 5 0 015 5v1h1a1 1 0 010 2h-1v2h-2v-2H9v2H7v-2H6a1 1 0 010-2h1v-1a5 5 0 015-5zm0 2a3 3 0 00-3 3v1h6v-1a3 3 0 00-3-3z" /></svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Form Konsultasi</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Isi kebutuhan Anda, tim kami akan follow up maksimal 1x24 jam.</p>
        <a href={contactHref} class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 transition hover:text-blue-700">Isi Formulir</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
